 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
+continue;
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){

 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :

 break;
 case '\"' :

 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :

 sb.append("\\>");

 sb.append(c);

 }
 break;

  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";

 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {

 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){

 switch (c){

 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);

 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;

  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 case '\r' :

------------Candidate---------------
 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
+int a=0;
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 sb.append(c);

 break;

  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {

 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }

 sb.append(backslashEscape);

 break;

 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
+sb.append(c);
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 static String strEscape(String s,char quote,String doublequoteEscape,String singlequoteEscape,String backslashEscape,CharsetEncoder outputCharsetEncoder){
 StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(s.length()+2);
 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
+assert (!s.isEmpty());
 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){
 if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();
 }

 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;

 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;

 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :

 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }else {

 }else {

  final String START_COMMENT="!--";

 sb.append("<\\");

 sb.append(quote);
 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 char c=s.charAt(i);
 switch (c){
 case '\0' :
 
 sb.append("\\0");
 break;
 case '\n' :
 
 sb.append("\\n");
 break;
 case '\r' :
 
 sb.append("\\r");
 break;
 case '\t' :
 
 sb.append("\\t");
 break;
 case '\\' :
 
 sb.append(backslashEscape);
 break;
 case '\"' :
 
 sb.append(doublequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 sb.append(singlequoteEscape);
 break;
 case '>' :
 
 if(i>=2&&((s.charAt(i-1)=='-'&&s.charAt(i-2)=='-')||(s.charAt(i-1)==']'&&s.charAt(i-2)==']'))){
 sb.append("\\>");
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 break;
 case '<' :
 
  final String END_SCRIPT="/script";
  final String START_COMMENT="!--";
 if(s.regionMatches(true,i+1,END_SCRIPT,0,END_SCRIPT.length())){
 sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(s.regionMatches(false,i+1,START_COMMENT,0,START_COMMENT.length())){
-sb.append("<\\");
+if(outputCharsetEncoder.canEncode(c)){
+sb.append(c);
+}else {
+appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
+}
 }else {
 sb.append(c);
 }
 }
 break;
 default :
 
 if(outputCharsetEncoder!=null){

-sb.append(c);
-}else {
-appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
-}
+sb.append("<\\");
 }else {
 if(c>0x1f&&c<=0x7f){
 sb.append(c);
 }else {
 appendHexJavaScriptRepresentation(sb,c);
 }
 }
 }
 }
 sb.append(quote);
 return sb.toString();

 for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++){
 switch (s.charAt(i)){
 case '"' :
 
 doubleq++;
 break;
 case '\'' :
 
 singleq++;
 break;
 }
 }

 quote='\'';

 }
